latestPosts.caption:
New to hoop? We got you! 

We’ve been making content here for almost 2 years now (😱) so we thought it was about time for a (re)introduction. 

So hello, we’re hoop 👋🏻

On Instagram, you know us as the makers of all things fitness content, and while that will continue to remain our identity, we thought we’d tell you about the part Instagram doesn’t really see.

Our purpose on Instagram, and in general, is to help India #LiveActive. Here, we do it through our bite-sized videos—and outside Instagram, we do it through our products, (available on hoophello.com) - all effective, natural, and amazing 🫡 

Swipe through to get to know us, our products, and what we stand for. Promise you won’t regret it! 🤩

And, as always, comment below for anything else you’d like to know about us!✨

#hoop #painrelief #musclerecovery #goodsleep #LiveActive
